title: 'Cron scheduler: run tracking and agent-aware triggers'
---
Extend scheduler.ml (already has SQLite + cron parsing) to: (1) track run history with timestamp/status/result preview, (2) expose 'cron runs' CLI command, (3) support per-agent routing so a job can target a specific named agent. No new deps.